{"tid":1082937,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撤資中國　降低虧損業務成本，Sony 決定關閉北京工廠轉移至泰國","createTime":"2019-03-29T09:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T11:13:04.000Z","uid":47714,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"75176c380d38ad8560ee009f48ed48177d0739f2","tid":1082937,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:15:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://finance.technews.tw/2019/03/28/sony-close-manufacture-in-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.technews.tw%2F2019%2F03%2F28%2Fsony-close-manufacture-in-china%2F&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HbTyP%2F9hhZoMZuVNmYF6dao%3D&h=d37f5f24\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.technews.tw/2019/03/28/sony-close-manufacture-in-china/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/01101106/428678315_c023482bf1_b-624x468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F01101106%2F428678315_c023482bf1_b-624x468.jpg&h=316713ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《路透社》最新報導，日本科技大廠 Sony 發言人 28 日表示，為了降低虧損，Sony 將在未來幾天關閉中國北京的智慧手機工廠。這也是繼日前南韓三星決定關閉天津工廠後，近期第 2 家決定將生產基地撤離中國的外商智慧型手機企業。<br />\n<br />\nSony 發言人指出，Sony 未來幾天將關閉中國北京的智慧手機生產工廠，把生產基地轉移到泰國工廠，以使成本減半，希望讓 Sony 智慧手機業務自 2020 年 4 月開始獲利。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，相較於遊戲機、電視、影像感測器等業務近年來有相對強勁的業績表現，Sony 智慧手機業務是少數虧損的業務。2018 年全球市占率約 1% 上下，本財年預計將虧損 950 億日圓，預計出貨量將為 700 萬支。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/06160916/全球唯一4K-HDR螢幕X-4K-HDR錄影的智慧手機Xperia-XZ2-Premium，帶來嶄新視覺享受，沉浸於最色彩迷人的影像體驗！-e1530864565180.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F06160916%2F%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%94%AF%E4%B8%804K-HDR%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95X-4K-HDR%E9%8C%84%E5%BD%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9FXperia-XZ2-Premium%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E5%B6%84%E6%96%B0%E8%A6%96%E8%A6%BA%E4%BA%AB%E5%8F%97%EF%BC%8C%E6%B2%89%E6%B5%B8%E6%96%BC%E6%9C%80%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E8%BF%B7%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97%EF%BC%81-e1530864565180.jpg&h=59d46c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為重組公司的獲利能力，Sony 近日正式宣布，將影像產品及解決方案業務（IP&amp;S）、家庭娛樂及音頻業務（HE&amp;S）和行動通訊業務（MC）重組為電子產品及解決方案業務部（EP&amp;S）。在新組織架構下，Sony 除了 PlayStation 遊戲機與遊戲開發業務仍由「索尼互動娛樂」（Sony Interactive Entertainment）運作，其餘硬體產品都將歸於同部門。這意味著 Sony 產品將盡可能去除過去部門間的隔閡和業務競爭，如手機照相功能的進化與相機業務的矛盾，也同時讓產品能進一步共享過去由不同部門管理的技術。<br />\n<br />\n（首圖來源：Flickr/Ian Muttoo CC BY 2.0）"},{"pid":"c3d1ee308a87c84385f06b4a4b2252336b20c21a","tid":1082937,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d364c85e55428e1cda1d48fe5b569d5001d898","tid":1082937,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T11:07:06.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"d98301e417ae0ca365f339b211f97cd060239afa","tid":1082937,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T11:10:53.000Z","msg":"共產黨：索尼罪大滔天"},{"pid":"dddd72bdb50cf06f026376f1838efd33e93c390d","tid":1082937,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T11:13:04.000Z","msg":"泰國工廠"}]}